                                  ተንቤን፡ በእዴሁ፡ ለአቡነ፡ መምህር፡ ገብረ፡ ወልድ፡ አጽምኡ፡</seg></q>
                                  <note>The letter summarizes the <foreign xml:lang="amh">hulatt lǝdat</foreign>doctrine.
                                  It was probably written by <persName ref="PRS9451Tewoflos"/> with his own hand, before his deposition
