                                <foreign xml:lang="am">ʾAbuna mamhǝr Gabra Wald </foreign> mentioned in the text
                                 is likely <persName ref="PRS13144GabraWald" role="owner">Gabra Wald</persName>,
                                  the owner of the manuscript.</note>

